					Mastodon
				</h2>
				{mastodonPost ? (
					<SocialCard {...mastodonPost} />
				) : (
					<div class="bg-gray-100 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 text-gray-500 italic">
						Unable to load recent post. Check back later!
					</div>
				)}
			</div>
			
			<div>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900 flex items-center gap-2">
					<svg class="w-6 h-6" viewBox="0 0 448 512" fill="currentColor"><path d="M331.5 235.7c2.2 .9 4.2 1.9 6.3 2.8 29.2 14.1 50.6 35.2 61.8 61.4 15.7 36.5 17.2 95.8-30.3 143.2-36.2 36.2-86.6 52.6-146.4 47.7-68.5-5.6-121-39.7-148.5-96.1-23.7-48.7-27.1-105-9.6-159.2C82.1 127 137.9 83 207 72.8c42-6 82.5 5.5 114 31 21.6 17.5 35.9 41.5 41.8 69.3 1.1 5.1 2 10.4 2.6 15.8 1.1 9.2-5.4 17.5-14.6 18.6-9.1 1.1-17.5-5.4-18.6-14.6-.4-3.3-1-6.6-1.8-9.8-4.5-21-15.4-39.4-31.8-52.7-24.6-20-56.1-29.2-88.7-24.5-53.9 7.9-97.4 42-108.4 97.4-13.6 68.3 10.8 135 64.9 174.5 46.2 33.7 105.7 40.5 158.1 18.2 55.4-23.5 83.2-83.3 64.2-140.2-12.9-38.6-39.9-63.5-76.8-70.1-29.8-5.4-59.5 2.1-80.4 21.2-22.1 20.3-33.8 52-32.9 89.2 .7 29.4 13.6 57 36.3 75.9 22.9 19.1 53 26.5 84.7 20.9 9.1-1.6 15.1-10.3 13.5-19.4-1.6-9.1-10.3-15.1-19.4-13.5-22.2 3.9-43.4-1.3-59.5-14.7-15.9-13.3-24.8-32.5-25.3-53.1-.7-26 7.4-48 22.7-62 13.5-12.3 32.5-17.2 51.6-13.7 21 3.8 35.2 16.7 41.9 37 13.9 41.5-6.5 84.5-47.5 102.5C240.2 396.1 196.5 385 168.3 351c-22.3-26.9-29.5-64.2-19.3-99.7 10.9-38 38-69.3 74.3-85.7 34.6-15.7 73-15.7 107.6 0l1 .5c8.3 3.9 18.1 .4 22-7.9s.4-18.1-7.9-22l-1-.5c-41.9-19-88.5-19-130.4 0-43.9 20-76.7 57.9-89.9 104-12.3 43-3.6 88.3 23.4 120.9 33.6 40.5 84.4 51.7 133.5 32.9 44-16.8 71.9-57 71.9-103.5 0-14.2-3-28-8.8-40.9-8.4-18.5-22.3-49.2-17.2-74.9-12.1-9.1 1.8-15.1 10.7-13.3 19.8 1.8 9.1 10.7 15.1 19.8 13.3 18-.3.5 36.3 3.7 52.4 12.8z"/></svg>
					Threads
				</h2>
				{threadsPost ? (
					<SocialCard {...threadsPost} />
				) : (
					<div class="bg-gray-100 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 text-gray-500 italic">
						Unable to load recent post. Check back later!
					</div>
				)}
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
